  "title": "Catering Sales Executive (Basic $3000-$4000 / 5 days / Clementi)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Catering Sales Executive (ID17047)<br>\nLocation: Clementi<br>\nWorking Hour: Mon to Fri, 9am-6.30pm<br>\nBasic Salary: $3000-$4000<br>\n*Benefits: AL 12days, Performance Bonus (Jan and July)<br>\n<br>\nJob Description<br>\n• Oversee the sales and profitability of event orders, ensuring smooth catering operations.<br>\n• Acquire new corporate clients through cold calling and sales visits.<br>\n• Stay informed about trends and developments in the catering industry.<br>\n• Handle telephone and online inquiries related to catering sales.<br>\n• Assist clients with professional event planning, packaging, and menu selection.<br>\n• Actively brainstorm creative ideas to enhance catering services for clients.<br>\n• Establish and nurture strong relationships with clients.</p>\n<p><br>\nRequirement:<br>\n• Minimum O Level / Diploma / Degree in Business or Marketing.<br>\n• At least 1-3 years of relevant sales experience in the Hotel Banquet/Catering/Event Sales industry.<br>\n• Proficient in English and Mandarin to effectively communicate with Mandarin-speaking clients.<br>\n• Possesses self-discipline, proactivity, and a strong sense of urgency.<br>\n• Must be self-motivated, dynamic, meticulous, creative, and sales oriented.<br>\n• Outgoing personality, highly motivated, able to work independently, and an inclusive team player.</p>",
